      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that will likely need attention in the near term. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including scratches and minor dents. The interior has visible wear and some minor damage. Overall, it is functional but will require some investment to bring it to a better standard.",
